dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""What about Revacholian traditions..."
dialogueTree.polish: „A co z revacholskimi tradycjami i zwyczajami?”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «А што наконт рэвашольскіх традыцый і звычаяў?»

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""Quite colourful in here... I mean..."
dialogueTree.english: "Quite colourful in here... I mean the lights!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Bardzo tu kolorowo... Mam na myśli światła!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: „Тут вельмі калярова... Я маю на ўвазе агні!”

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""I don't mean to sound paranoid or..."
dialogueTree.english: "I don't mean to sound paranoid or anything, *but*..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie chcę brzmieć jak paranoik czy coś, *ale*...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Не хачу гучаць, як параноік ці нешта такое, *але*...»

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""Gotta be careful what you say thes..."
dialogueTree.english: "Gotta be careful what you say these days."
dialogueTree.polish: „Trzeba uważać w tych czasach na to, co się mówi”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Трэба быць асцярожным у гэтыя часы ў тым, што кажаш».

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""It's not like I go to meetings or..."
dialogueTree.english: "It's not like I go to meetings or anything."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie, żebym chodził na spotkania czy coś w tym stylu”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Не, каб я хадзіў на сустрэчы або нешта ў гэтым стылі».

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""Mass-radio can't be trusted. They'..."
dialogueTree.english: "Mass-radio can't be trusted. They're all just mouth-pieces."
dialogueTree.polish: „Masowym audycjom radiowym nie można ufać. To tylko propagandowa tuba”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Масавым радыёпраграмам нельга давяраць. Гэта толькі прапагандысцкая труба».

dialogueTree.title: Gary, the Cryptofascist: ""If I come to *your* home I respect..."
dialogueTree.english: "If I come to *your* home I respect your way of life, right?"
dialogueTree.polish: „Gdy przychodzi się do *czyjegoś* domu, to szanuje się czyjś styl życia, prawda?”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Калі прыходзіш у *чужы* дом, то паважаеш чужы лад жыцця, праўда?»
